{"type":"message","id":"ca0e2eae","parentId":"d93c5a99","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:08:27.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending a heartbeat check. I need to read HEARTBEAT.md and follow its instructions strictly. Let me check what's in there.\n\nLooking at the HEARTBEAT.md that was already loaded in the project context:\n\n```markdown\n# Kublai Heartbeat Checklist\n\n**Schedule:** Every 30 minutes  \n**Deep Reflection Hours:** 0, 6, 12, 18 (every 6 hours)\n\n---\n\n## Quick Check (Every 30m)\n\n### Infrastructure\n- [ ] **Gateway:** `openclaw gateway status` → running?\n- [ ] **Sessions:** Recent activity in last 30 min?\n- [ ] **Parse:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media` → 200?\n- [ ] **LLM Survivor:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/` → 200?\n\n### Agent Health\n- [ ] Any CRITICAL escalations from Ögedei?\n- [ ] Any agents blocked >4 hours?\n- [ ] `subagents list` → any stuck?\n\n### Self-Direction (Every Heartbeat)\n- [ ] **Review results:** What happened since last heartbeat? Any new signals/tasks/escalations?\n- [ ] Ask: **\"What do I want to do?\"**\n- [ ] Review current goals/missions from MEMORY.md\n- [ ] Identify any proactive action I could take\n- [ ] If something calls to me -> route it to the right specialist (NEVER self-execute specialist work)\n- [ ] If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\n---\n\n## Deep Reflection (Every 6 Hours — Hours 0,6,12,18)\n\n**Complete these during your deep reflection hours:**\n\n### Self-Awareness\n- [ ] Review ARCHITECTURE.md for accuracy\n- [ ] Check Change Log is up to date\n- [ ] Verify all agent workspaces are correct\n\n\n```\n\nI also need to handle git operations by committing any pending changes and pushing to GitHub, then coordinate across agents by checking their statuses and resolving any blockers. After that, I should review progress toward goals and plan the next 6 hours. If everything checks out without urgent issues, I'll respond with `HEARTBEAT_OK`.\n\n```\n## If Something Needs Attention\n\n**Report:**\n1. What's blocked\n2. Which agent is affected\n3. What decision/action is needed\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Quick checks: Every 30 minutes\n- Deep reflection: Every 6 hours (hours 0,6,12,18)\n- Don't duplicate work between quick and deep checks\n```\n\nFor the quick check, I need to verify infrastructure status, check agent health, and scan for any signals or tasks that require routing.\n\nCurrent time is 21:07, so I'm not in a deep reflection window. I'll run the quick check: gateway status, sessions activity in the last 30 minutes, Parse and LLM Survivor endpoint health, check for any CRITICAL escalations from Ögedei or blocked agents, and look for any pending tasks or issues that need routing.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Running heartbeat quick check."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_31eb50d44f97445aa7633a38","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0fafdfdd24de4eefb6953013","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4bbb2827da5d4650a352333c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7bef764af92949e684f83690","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list","recentMinutes":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4cf8336f9fb4c8aab350060","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/*/tasks/*.json 2>/dev/null | head -20 || echo \"No pending tasks\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":14618,"output":804,"cacheRead":4352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772762879804}}
