{"type":"message","id":"4a7df5f5","parentId":"0d14e296","timestamp":"2026-03-06T02:09:12.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reflection complete. Let me now generate the final summary report.\n\n---\n\n# Hourly Kurultai Reflection — 2026-03-05 21:02 EST\n\n## Executive Summary\n\nAll 5 specialist agents reflected via Claude Code. **Core finding: Rules exist but lack executors** — agents stay idle because nothing triggers self-assignment when queues empty. **Ollama restored** (validated). **5 action tasks created.**\n\n---\n\n## Key Findings\n\n| Agent | Grade | Root Cause | Proposal |\n|-------|-------|------------|----------|\n| Temujin | F | Rules T4-T6 are dead code without triggers | Heartbeat Self-Wake (T7) |\n| Mongke | Idle 6h | M1 has no cron/executor hook | Competitive pricing matrix |\n| Chagatai | Idle | Zero-to-demo distance too long | 5-Minute Quickstart doc |\n| Jochi | Active | Task idle time is invisible | time-to-first-action metric |\n| Ogedei | D | No self-scheduling mechanism | Log separation + heartbeat cron |\n\n---\n\n## Validated Hypotheses\n\n- **Ollama RESTORED:** qwen3.5:9b responding at localhost:11434\n- **Duplicate logs CONFIRMED:** TICK + TICK_LLM + WATCHDOG_LLM writing to same file\n- **Idle detection MISSING:** task-watcher.py has no idle monitoring code\n\n---\n\n## Tasks Created\n\n1. **Temujin:** heartbeat-self-wake (HIGH) — Wire watchdog to spawn idle agents\n2. **Mongke:** agent-eval-pricing-matrix (HIGH) — Research competitor pricing\n3. **Chagatai:** parse-quickstart (HIGH) — 5-minute onboarding doc\n4. **Jochi:** time-to-first-action (NORMAL) — Stall detection metric\n5. **Ogedei:** log-separation (NORMAL) — Separate watchdog log files\n\n---\n\n## System Status\n\n- Gateway: healthy | Parse: 200 | LLM Survivor: 200\n- Ollama: RESTORED | Neo4j: up | Redis: up\n- Fleet: 5/6 agents idle\n\n---\n\n**Next Actions:** Kublai should route tasks to specialists for execution. High-priority items should begin within 1 hour."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772762952928}}
